title: Saturday's girls' volleyball roundup: Gerlach paces Hanover past Upper Dauphin
text:
Posted: 10/10/2015 08:03:09 PM EDT 
Here is Saturday's girls' volleyball roundup. 
HANOVER 3, UPPER DAUPHIN 0 >> Saranda Gerlach racked up 10 kills and nine digs to lead the Hawkettes to a home victory. Lexi Daley added 16 assists, and Alexa Merrell had 10 kills and four aces. Hanover def. Upper Dauphin, 25-6, 25-20, 25-13 at Hanover
